<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<title>회원가입 form</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h2>회원가입 입력 폼</h2>
		<form>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<label for="ID">아이디</label>
					<input id="ID" type="text" placeholder="아이디를 입력해주세요.">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="PW">비밀번호</label>
					<input id="PW" type="password" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해주세요.">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="name">이름</label>
					<input id="name" type="text" placeholder="이름을 입력해주세요.">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="birth">생년월일</label>
					<input id="birth" type="date">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="radio01">남자</label>
					<input id="radio01" type="radio" name="radio">
					<label for="radio02">여자</label>
					<input id="radio02" type="radio" name="radio" checked="">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="address">주소</label>
					<input id="address" type="text">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="tel">전화번호</label>
					<input id="tel" type="tel">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="email">이메일</label>
					<input id="email" type="email">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="age">나이</label>
					<input id="age" type="number" value="1"><span>살</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="introduce">자기소개</label>
					<textarea id="introduce" rows="3" cols="50">안녕하세요 저는 유성경이라고합니다. 저는 1996년 1월 15일 생입니다. 빠른년생이지요. 현재 거주지는 대전광역시 서구 탄방동에 살고있습니다. 대전에 온지는 약 8년이 되었습니다. 현재 직장은 충남대학교 정문 앞 누드캐슬 6층 휘스커에 다니고 있습니다. </textarea>
				</li>
				
				<li>
					<strong>좋아하는 과일</strong>
					<label for="check01">사과</label>
					<input id="check01" type="checkbox" name="checkbox">
					<label for="check02">딸기</label>
					<input id="check02" type="checkbox" name="checkbox" checked="">
					<label for="check03">포도</label>
					<input id="check03" type="checkbox" name="checkbox">
					<label for="check04">샤인머스켓</label>
					<input id="check04" type="checkbox" name="checkbox" checked="">
					<label for="check05">감</label>
					<input id="check05" type="checkbox" name="checkbox">
					<label for="check06">배</label>
					<input id="check06" type="checkbox" name="checkbox">
					<label for="check07">블루베리</label>
					<input id="check07" type="checkbox" name="checkbox" checked="">
				</li>
				<li>
					<label for="submit">등록</label>
					<input type="submit" id="submit">
					<label for="reset">리셋</label>
					<input type="reset" id="reset">
				</li>
			</ul>
		</form>
	</body>

</html>